            "title": "盤中速報 - Cadence設計系統(CDNS-US)大漲5%，報333.84美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Cadence設計系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDNS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDNS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDNS-US</a>)截至台北時間04日04:22股價上漲15.9美元，報333.84美元，漲幅5%，成交量1,410,795（股），盤中最高價333.84美元、最低價315.68美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.92%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.39%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.33%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.7%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Cadence設計系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDNS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDNS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDNS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.96%</li> <li>近 1 月：-7.69%</li> <li>近 3 月：-9.68%</li> <li>近 6 月：+5.84%</li> <li>今年以來：+4.02%</li></ul></section></main>",
